overview: Under The Order's guidance, innocent Elder White is quickly learning he's an insatiable bottom. Now that he's been initiated, he's thirsty for even more intense experiences. During Elder White's initiation, he has forged bonds of love with his priesthood leaders. Now it's time for him to make the Covenant that will seal his membership in The Order. He's become an expert at riding dick, and he's determined to earn the respect of President Oaks and Nelson. How far will he go to please his leaders?
title: Elder White: Chapters 5-8
